(94, 'The Board delegates oversight of certain risk topics and themes to sub-committees and the day-to-day management of the NDA group to the executive team', ' control and governance. The committee oversees audit and financial reporting', ' advises and reports on the plans', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, ' comprising the Group Chief Executive and other senior executives. Chair Audit and Risk Assurance Committee(A&RAC) The committee provides advice and assurance to the Board on risk', ' and provides an assessment of assurance reliability and integrity. The committee oversees the effectiveness and quality of the group risk management framework and monitors risk exposure against group risk appetite. Non-Executive Board Member Nominations ', ' advise on the structure and size of the committees', 0),
(95, 'Group Chief Executive Officer & Accounting Officer Executive Committees Purpose Meeting Chair Executive Committee Accountable for implementing strategy and plans approved by Board. Includes sanction and decision making. Group Chief Executive Officer Execu', ' processes and practices and monitor risk exposure against group risk appetite. To monitor and manage risk and assurance mechanisms. To monitor findings from audit and assurance reviews. To advise the Board A&RAC. Group Director of Risk and Assurance Fina', ' including programmes', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, ' Risk and Assurance Committee To oversee the effectiveness and quality of the group risk management framework', ' procurements', ' IT expenditure', 0),
