(97, 'manufacturing and engineering businesses. Her current portfolio includes non-executive', ' Computacenter plc', ' the chemicals company Victrex plc and the specialised steel company Aperam SA. She has also held a range of other board roles with private and listed companies including ConvaTec plc', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, ' senior independent director and committee chair roles variously for Defence Equipment and Support (DE&S) within the Ministry of Defence', ' RPC Group plc', ' Ceva Logistics and Rexam plc.', 0),
(98, 'Ros also plays important roles in the charity sector and academia. She was Non-Executive Director of the â€˜Your Lifeâ€™ initiative', ' industry- sponsored campaign to increase take up of maths and physics amongst 14-16 year-olds; Deputy Chair of Southampton University', ' and was the first chair of the Universityâ€™s HSE & Risk Audit and Assurance; and is on the board of the community interest company Eton Community CIC. Ros was awarded an honorary doctorate in 2015 for services to industry and to the voluntary sector. He', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, ' which was a Government led', ' walking', ' music and theatre. Ros is married with 4 children.', 0),
(99, 'His roles included Head of BP Group Investor Relations', ' Deputy Head of Global Exploration and Production', ' Head of BP Group Planning', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, ' Commercial Director of BP Chemicals', ' he was BPâ€™s lead Director on the board of TNK-BP and Chairman of its Health', ' Safety and Environment Committee.', 0),
